'''Serowe''' ke motse mogolo wa morafe wa [[Bangwato]] o kgosi kgolo ya bone e leng Kgosi Seretse Khama Ian Khama. Bangwe ba bagaka ba morafe o ke Rre Ratsie Setlhako, Kgosi Gorewang Kgamane, Rre Seretse khama le ba bangwe fela jalo [http://www.en.wikipedia.org/Botswana Botswana].

Serowe o itsege thata fa ele motse mogolo mo Botswana morago ga motse mogolo wa Bakwena ebong Molepolole ebile ke one motse mogolo wa Bamangwato. Serowe o itsege thata ka ele one motse yoo bontsi jwa  botautona ba Botswana ba tswang teng.

==Ditso==

Serowe o ntse o gakologelwa Khama III,kgosi ya Bamangwatobatho ba bogologolo ka ngwagakgolo lesome le boferabongwe le masome mabedi.Ka ngwaga wa 1903 o ne a thomiwa fa e le motse mogolo  Serowe, Bamangwato.New International Encyclopedia.Gape ke lefelo la matsalo la ga  [[Seretse Khama]],motswana wa ntlha President,le setso sa morafe wa letso la Bamangwato.

Sekolo sa Swaneng Hill e ne e le dingwe tsa dikolo tsa  ntlha mo Serowe tsa Brigades Movement dikolo di simolotswe ke morutegi Patrick van Rensburg.

==Lefelo==
